00:40:36,934 --> 00:40:38,524
Mu-yeong!

408
00:40:41,897 --> 00:40:43,017
Mu-yeong!

409
00:40:44,900 --> 00:40:46,070
Mu-yeong!

410
00:40:53,742 --> 00:40:54,952
Tuanku.

411
00:40:57,621 --> 00:40:58,661
Tuanku...

412
00:41:03,085 --> 00:41:04,375
Tuanku.

